pulses.name: 20241122 Most Active Threat Indicators
pulses.description:
22 Nov 2024 : Most Active Threat Indicators
#Cybersecurity #Cyberattack #RCE #Botnet #IOC

Top 3 Source Countries:

- United States (US) - The US is the primary source of cyber activities, with numerous instances of botnets like SystemBC, various remote code execution vulnerabilities, and scanning activities indicating a high level of cyber threat activity.
- China (CN) - China is frequently associated with multiple attacks, particularly targeting D-Link devices and GPON routers, showcasing its involvement in a wide range of cyber threats.
- India (IN) - India appears prominently in the data, primarily linked to various remote command execution vulnerabilities and attacks on network devices, indicating a substantial presence in the cyber threat landscape.
